s from viable\nphysical theories. We advocate the EFT approach as a way to constrain new\nphysics from future large-scale-structure data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 9 Jun 2015 19:10:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 10 Jul 2015 10:46:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-03"}
