tropy and its one-loop\nquantum correction, after imposing a new set of monodromy conditions. The\nholographic classical result matches exactly with the leading contribution in\nthe field theory up to $e^{-4\\pi TR}$ and $l^6$, while the holographical\none-loop contribution is in exact agreement with next-to-leading results in\nfield theory up to $e^{-\\frac{6\\pi TR}{n}}$ and $l^4$ as well.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 10 Jun 2015 08:25:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2015 12:49:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-11"}
